Implement HeapSort: Implement the HeapSort algorithm to sort an array.

Kth Largest Element in an Array: Find the kth largest element in an unsorted array.

Top K Frequent Elements: Find the k most frequent elements in an array.

Merge K Sorted Lists: Merge k sorted linked lists into one sorted list.

Sort Nearly Sorted Array: Sort an array where each element is at most k positions away from its sorted position.

Find Median in a Stream: Design a data structure to find the median in a stream of integers.

Running Median: Find the median as you process elements in an array.

Maximum Element of Each Subarray of Size K: Find the maximum element in each subarray of size k.

Connect "n" Ropes with Minimum Cost: Connect ropes with minimum cost.

Smallest Range in K Lists: Find the smallest range that includes at least one element from each of the K lists.

Find k Closest Points to Origin: Find the k closest points to the origin in a 2D plane.

Sort Characters by Frequency: Sort characters in a string based on their frequency.

Kth Smallest Element in a Sorted Matrix: Find the kth smallest element in a sorted matrix.

Super Ugly Number: Find the nth super ugly number based on a list of primes.

Sort Integers by The Number of 1 Bits: Sort integers based on the number of 1's in their binary representation.
